title: Ragetooth Temple
story: The temple is situated high in the Stormspear mountains. Lately a fearsome basilisk has made its lair here.

notes.text: A notable stone gate with a keyhole to the south.
A basket containing an iron key.
A chainmail at the bottom of a pool.
A medium chest holds a mysterious, covered with carvings flail.
An uncanny, singing relic in the middle of a pentagram on the ground.
